### 3.2 Accessibility


The existing design overlooks some accessibility standards crucial for users with disabilities, including color contrast and screen reader compatibility.


### 3.3 Aesthetic Design


Stylistic elements do not fully reflect our brand ethos of warmth and healing, often leaning towards sterile and cold visuals.


